message: I'm sitting at work, spring snowstorm blowing around outside and I've decided that the only way this day can be salvaged is by having dill pickle chips for lunch. WACKY.
Also, winter sucks. I think I should throw a Mexican beach party at my house to alleviate the OMG WINTER GRARR feelings.
If it makes you feel any better, it's heading to the upper 70's here in Virginia.
